JSFlive JSF 2.2: Configurable resource directory
================================================

This is example jsf22-resource-dir from Michael Kurz's JSFlive post on JSF 2.2
Configurable resource directory:
http://jsflive.wordpress.com/2013/04/01/jsf22-config-resource-dir

It can be started directly with the Maven Jetty Plugin. Simply call the following command:
mvn jetty:run
